        <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">
            @Constants.SERVICE_NAME (Home Upgrade Grant)
        </h1>

        <p class="govuk-body">
            The Home Upgrade Grant scheme provides funding for local authorities to improve the energy performance and
            heating for homes that do not have gas boilers.
        </p>

        <p class="govuk-body">
            If you are eligible we will send your answers to your local authority who will contact you for further
            information and book a home survey.
        </p>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Use this service to:</h2>

        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
            <li>Check if you are eligible for the scheme</li>
            <li>Submit your information to your local authority</li>
            <li>Get help in other ways to upgrade your home</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">Who is eligible for this grant</h2>
        <p class="govuk-body">
            Homeowners with a property:
        </p>
        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
            <li>in England</li>
            <li>without a gas boiler</li>
            <li>with an EPC rating of D, E, F, or G</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What the grant could cover</h2>

        <p class="govuk-body">
            If you are eligible, a surveyor will look at how your home can conserve more energy, and reduce your bills.
            These could include:
        </p>
        <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
            <li>wall, loft and underfloor insulation</li>
            <li>new air source heat pumps or electric radiators</li>
        </ul>

        <a href="@Url.Action(nameof(QuestionnaireController.GasBoiler_Get), "Questionnaire")" role="button" draggable="false" class="govuk-button govuk-!-margin-top-2 govuk-!-margin-bottom-8 govuk-button--start" data-module="govuk-button">
